definitions.definition: The number 10 100 {\displaystyle 10^{100}} , or ten to the power of a hundred . Equivalent to ten duotrigintillion (short scale), or ten sexdecilliard (long scale).

main_definition: The number 10 100 {\displaystyle 10^{100}} , or ten to the power of a hundred . Equivalent to ten duotrigintillion (short scale), or ten sexdecilliard (long scale). [from 1920.]
